    "Thus, ρ n ∈ 1 n B L ∞ (Q) ∩ Em(P d) and the definition of strong nonsurjectivity is thus verified.",
    "The Flat Chain Conjecture of Lang in all dimensions and codimensionsThe purpose of this section is to prove Theorem 1.7.",
